text:
Ever since 
I've heard 
that you can tell 
if a person is loyal
by the warmth in his hands, 
I've bought
the finest wool 
in the city
and started weaving
a pair of gloves 
for you. 
It isn't that 
I don't trust you, 
It's just that 
the season is here.
❄☃️
